  "Description": {
    "English": "Equip this exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Personal Flair</span> in commemoration of the 'Blighted' <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Expedition</span>, the glorious retrieval of ill-gotten lucre, and the discovery of a pirate secret.<br><br>Apply this banner to your profile at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "装备上这枚专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">个人旗帜</span>，纪念你完成“瘟疫侵扰”<span class=\"name name-stellar\">远征</span>，光荣追回不义之财并发现了一个海盗的秘密。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>中将这面旗帜应用至你的个人档案。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "裝備這款特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">個人造型</span>紀念「毀滅殆盡」<span class=\"name name-stellar\">探險</span>的完成、獲取不義之財的榮耀，以及海盜秘密的發現。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>將此旗幟套用至你的檔案。"
  },
